{"tid":1938554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺底下，呢個方法或者係一個抗爭出路？","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T10:52:54.000Z","uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea13ced414f9e25dead506dd4ad1d78585a919bd","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"武肺越爆越勁，出街發夢個風險高左（無論係比狗咬或者𡃤武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動好似比武肺cut停左咁，我地都好似無哂創意，唔知仲可以做咩<br />\n但作為和理非好自然諗啲仆街縮骨野，同埋想有靚既畫面打國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我諗起一樣野：戰時撒傳單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以前打仗果時 都好興去人地地方撒傳單，勸人投降講自己國家有幾好之類，我地而家都係打緊仗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果香港一夜之間 遍地充滿文宣 個畫面又會點樣？好似之前人鏈同10點怒吼咁，香港人齊心同時間做一件事，效果可以好驚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大概方法：每月一日（21日或者31日最好），特定時間（夜晚9點）<br />\n<br />\n每人至少準備一張文宣，係制高點/街/商場同時間一齊投放</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果揀31日揀，全港9點同時有831打死人既文宣係全港飄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 更加be water 防不勝防<br />\n2. 抗疫不忘抗爭<br />\n3. 視覺效果大<br />\n4. 連儂牆2.0<br />\n<br />\n危機：<br />\n1. 比cam影到<br />\n2. 罰1500，公屋扣分<br />\n3. 比環保L屌到仆街<br />\n4. 執死清潔工<br />\n5. 社會混亂，周街飄影響到車/人<br />\n6. 留指紋（帶手套基本野啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔到，大家有興趣可以一齊討論，好似之前人鏈都係慢慢傾定砌出黎，有興趣可以再開其他post討論<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔洗急，唔洗日日做，每個月爆佢一鑊 光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有心人一齊諗詳細啲睇下有無得搞下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近排大家都咁灰 連登又咁多pr 咁多分化，係時候做下野喇"},{"pid":"66af354ea3fb4f3b5180ae439bcf0f6723bb62e2","tid":1938554,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"有諗法 幫推"},{"pid":"8588c3aa46e867a7adf0eb6216e88e068d5bc2eb","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66af354ea3fb4f3b5180ae439bcf0f6723bb62e2","tid":1938554,"uid":311486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"有諗法 幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b053488ce682aedefc7cfb48138c55b6c0e800","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:03:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89ffb337e485c6a19a6935723bb03dc7172c2753","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4777ffd1754f1697e7af1459d1fbdfc4146cf20a","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T18:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f7aa4da14079a5004f5c708fb2c9e1d755b0b9b","tid":1938554,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}